The previous stream was a guerrilla preparing for this stream: Usada Buildings Interview.
This is the reborn for U-pa-ru-pa duet. It passed a time since that August 2020 with the first "Clubhouse 51" delivery.
Along with that stream and this, both have "Splatoon 2", "Granny Simulator" and "Super Bunny Man", where the first mentioned was their gameplay debut.

Along with traps and jokes, these things worth it for a nice ending. :_ハート:
